short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Leetcode stats and motivation to code daily

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension built to motivate you to solve a coding problem daily, as simple as name of the extension Code Daily with LeetCode. You can either solve a preselected question or choose from any topic and difficulty of your choice
